SliTaz PiTFT Touchscreen
------------------------

SliTaz runs nicely on PiTFT! Here is a custom flavor to get started.
Cross compiling the fbtft kernel driver is done with:

# sat-rpi cook-linux --clean --gconfig --fbtft 

Then enable video drivers you want, close te config and it will buid.
The default X session is powered by sts.


Adafruit Fork of FBTFT for use with Adafruit TS shield
------------------------------------------------------
https://github.com/adafruit/adafruit-rpi-fbtft/


Adafruit guides
---------------
https://learn.adafruit.com/adafruit-pitft-28-inch-resistive-touchscreen-display-raspberry-pi

